WEBVTT

00:00:00.366 --> 00:00:01.980
-S, VLINUS LITVA.

00:00:07.673 --> 00:00:10.029
in shpitol hot men mir zeyer gikh oysgeheylt.

00:00:10.069 --> 00:00:13.708
ikh bin gelegn dort emes bay a tsvey a halb monat, biz dray monat tsayt,

00:00:13.900 --> 00:00:16.537
un m'iz gekumen tsu geyn in shtub, di froy hot mir gebrakht

00:00:16.537 --> 00:00:19.732
tsu geyn in sh- tsu f- tsu firn in shtub shoyn oyf mayne fis.

00:00:20.363 --> 00:00:23.929
un ikh hob nor dokh hob ikh zikh geshpirt moralish zeyer gesh- zeyer

00:00:23.929 --> 00:00:31.950
zeyer shtark dershlogn der- farshlogn. tsu arbet hob ikh shoyn nit gekent geyn vayter, un ikh hob shoyn nit gevelt geyn tsu der arbet, vayl ikh hob farshtanen az di batsiung

00:00:31.956 --> 00:00:42.041
tsu di arbeter velkhe arbetn in dem ministorn-kabinet zaynen di zeyer nit nit m'bahandlt ver- vern bahandlt nit vi keyn mentshn.

00:00:44.781 --> 00:00:52.234
un ikh hob ongehoybn zikh farnemen mit literatur. in di fraye tsayt fleg ikh shraybn in yidishe tsaytungen,

00:00:52.780 --> 00:00:57.341
in a sakh eyropeishe tsaytungen fleg ikh shraybn. in Parizher Tsaytung fleg ikh shraybn.

00:00:57.341 --> 00:01:02.021
in Erets-Yisroeldike Tsaytung, di nayes, hob ikh geshribn farshidene reportazhn.

00:01:04.120 --> 00:01:08.630
ikh hob geshribn mayne farsheydene, ikh hob ongehoybn shraybn dikhtung, farsheydene lider,

00:01:08.630 --> 00:01:14.744
velkhe ikh hob frier gekent s'mir oysgekumen in in oyfn oyfn geza- oyfn gedank.

00:01:14.829 --> 00:01:24.829
un ikh mit dem hob ikh a bisl zikh fargesn ale mayne vaytokn un ikh hob bashlosn az ikh vel,

00:01:24.829 --> 00:01:30.744
ikh bin dan dan ersht geven zibn un fuftsik yor. keyn gantse keyn zekhtsik hob ikh hob ikh nokh nit der- der- der- dertsoygn

00:01:30.744 --> 00:01:33.797
keyn pensye hob ikh, keyn pe- keyn pensyoner bin ikh nit geven.

00:01:34.022 --> 00:01:43.179
nor az ikh bin shoyn gevorn zekhtsik yor, trakht ikh, nu ikh vel shoyn mer mit arbet mistome mer nit kenen geyn. ikh vel zikh farnemen mit bay mit mayn neygung tsu literatur.

00:01:44.451 --> 00:01:54.083
nu mayne a- mayne artiklen hobn mir hobn gehat a gants groysn derfolg. m'hot di di redaktorn fun Varshever Tsaytung, Katarko, hot mir nit eyn mol geshribn

00:01:54.083 --> 00:01:58.890
er hot gebetn ikh zol shraybn, er hot iz do gekumen bay mir tsu gast tsu forn fun Varshe

00:01:58.930 --> 00:02:06.180
tsu mir shtub, un er hot mir zikh interesirt vegn mir. er flegt drukn ale mayne lider, s'nit geven keyn eyn eyn eyn gedikht vos er zol nit drukn.

00:02:09.797 --> 00:02:14.595
un dos iz farshteyt zikh, oder haynt tsum tog, ot di letste tsayt,

00:02:14.595 --> 00:02:19.297
bin ikh vider krank gevorn do, ikh bin gelegn oyfn bet a lange tsayt, onderhalbn yor tsayt bin ikh gelegn tsu,

00:02:19.297 --> 00:02:22.255
ikh hob gerufn bay mir kentik di ale iberlebenishn fun di lagern,

00:02:22.255 --> 00:02:24.616
di ale veytokn vos ikh hob gehat. ikh fleg zen yedn ikh fleg

00:02:24.616 --> 00:02:27.127
shpirn yedn tog di veytokn fun di fun di fun di hent

00:02:27.127 --> 00:02:30.787
un fun ti- fun dem brust-kastn b- beys ikh bin gelegn, gehongen oyf di shtrik.

00:02:30.787 --> 00:02:33.956
ikh fleg zen bay nakht, ikh fleg s'flegt mikh shteyn alts far di oygn.

00:02:34.367 --> 00:02:40.368
un ikh hob zikh zeyer shtark tsebrokhn, ikh bin gelegn a lange tsayt biz hayntike yor,

00:02:40.577 --> 00:02:44.064
fun fir un nayntsikstn bizn zeks un nayntsikstn, dort bin ikh kimat nit aroys fun shtub.

00:02:44.458 --> 00:02:45.532
nor ikh fleg shraybn.

00:02:46.264 --> 00:02:53.463
di letste fleg ikh zikh farnemen mi- mit in fleg ikh arbetn mitarbetn tsvishn di doktoyrim fun fun meditsinishn tsenter tsu di bay di yidishe gemeynde,

00:02:53.503 --> 00:02:56.478
ikh hob dortn gehat oykh a interes tsum arbetn, mir flegn helfn dortn yidn.

00:02:56.478 --> 00:02:59.741
oreme yidn, kranke yidn, mit meditsin, mit medikamen.

00:02:59.815 --> 00:03:04.635
ikh hob dortn farnumen oykh als sekretar fun dem meditsi- fun dem fun dem komitet fun fun dem rat fun dem

00:03:04.793 --> 00:03:07.774
meditsinishn tsenter bay dokter Zak UNK.

00:03:10.210 --> 00:03:14.624
nokh hayntike yor, fun onfang yor shoyn,

00:03:14.867 --> 00:03:18.489
hob ikh dershpirt az ikh ken nokh epes vos iz ton.

00:03:21.938 --> 00:03:27.433
nu ikh ken do oysleyenen mayne a a dikht UNK, oyber, yo.

00:03:25.718 --> 00:03:27.264
bite sheyn.

00:03:39.015 --> 00:03:43.247
ikh hob ongeshribn far der tsayt fil dikhtn, farsheydene mit farsheydene temes.

00:03:43.247 --> 00:03:47.295
nor ikh volt voln oder tsum tog peysekh oder tsum tog purim.

00:03:48.310 --> 00:03:57.515
mayn baym bruder-keyver iz do aza min. di di lid hot ge- di dikht hot men gedrukt in a yidisher tsaytung in Ostralyen,

00:03:57.515 --> 00:04:00.103
der redaktor hot geshribn tsu mir ikh zol vayter shraybn.

00:04:00.345 --> 00:04:01.908
ot ken ikh ir iberleyenen.

00:04:04.378 --> 00:04:07.784
ikh hob dir oyf krumike vegn getrofn,

00:04:08.412 --> 00:04:11.224
un hob in dayn lebn a vogler derzen.

00:04:11.685 --> 00:04:14.548
es zaynen di teg dayne blinde farlofn,

00:04:14.672 --> 00:04:17.551
in nakhtikn blondzhen bagleyt dir dayn pen.

00:04:18.688 --> 00:04:22.159
ver binstu, farlozener, eynzamer vogler?

00:04:22.789 --> 00:04:25.736
mit zorgfule kneytshn in shtern gefarbt,

00:04:26.046 --> 00:04:29.077
tsi brent in dayn hartsn der vint fun a odler,

00:04:29.320 --> 00:04:33.583
tsi zingt in dayn sk- in tsi zingt shoyn in skeynes dayn shotn geshtalt?

00:04:33.792 --> 00:04:36.843
vos zukhstu oyf vegn oyf blotike roye,

00:04:36.843 --> 00:04:39.475
vos shlingstu UNK dorshtik a yetvider roysh?

00:04:39.475 --> 00:04:45.294
dertseyln di himlen farveytikte, groye, az eybik vet ful zayn mit trern dayn kos.

00:04:46.026 --> 00:04:48.753
tsi glet dir der vint dayne hor azoy tsartik,

00:04:48.844 --> 00:04:51.538
tsi hot dir farkisheft der foygl-gezang?

00:04:51.780 --> 00:04:54.646
tsi vunken dir frukhtn shoyn tsaytike fartik,

00:04:54.646 --> 00:04:57.377
vos nem zey nit raysn, es tut zey nor bang.

00:04:58.193 --> 00:05:01.798
iz ver binstu dokh, du farneplter vogler?

00:05:01.922 --> 00:05:04.852
tsi kon ikh dergreykhn dayn umklorn ⟨gnor⟩,

00:05:05.112 --> 00:05:07.097
du fregst un du blondzhest.

00:05:07.204 --> 00:05:12.413
farvoglerster vogler, far zikh un far yenem an entfer shoyn do.

00:05:17.228 --> 00:05:18.178
dos alts.

00:05:18.178 --> 00:05:23.769
ikh hob do farsheydene lider, ober s'do s'do viln ikh hob keyn tsayt un der viln tsu dertseyln tsu tsu leyenen.

00:05:23.640 --> 00:05:28.578
du voltst gekent zogn vos vilt ir zogn tsu di kumendike doyrim?

00:05:32.112 --> 00:05:34.513
nu, mayn eyntsike farlang iz,

00:05:34.513 --> 00:05:39.699
ikh ze in di kum- in di kumendike doyres ze ikh mayne kinder, mayn zun un mayn tokhter. ikh hob a zun,

00:05:39.925 --> 00:05:43.288
im iz shoyn bald fertsik yor. di tokhter mayne iz

00:05:43.288 --> 00:05:54.679
zibn un tsvontsik shoyn, vert oykh in gikhn zibn un tsvontsik yor. zey hobn nit gevust zey hobn zey veysn nit zey hobn zey veysn nit vegn di g- vegn di laydn fun zayne fun zeyere fun zeyer eltern, zey veysn nit di laydn fun zeyer folk.

00:05:54.679 --> 00:06:01.099
ikh vel zey veltn vintshn, nit nor mayne kinder nor ale kinder, fun undzer folk un fun ale felker,

00:06:01.099 --> 00:06:06.921
zey zoln oysmaydn di ale di ale laydn, di ale tsores vos mir hobn gehat in undzer tsayt.

00:06:09.557 --> 00:06:10.769
a groysn dank.
